# Update the herdr-orchestration skill with the ping-based monitoring loop

## Step

Rewrite the "Monitoring (the steering loop)" section of `~/.claude/skills/herdr-orchestration/SKILL.md` around `herdr-ping-wait` as the primary mechanism for pi workers: the `run_in_background` invocation, harvesting the event JSON (including `last_message_tail`), re-arming for the next turn, and the fallback ladder (`herdr agent wait` / shepherd for non-pi panes and `pane_gone`). Only document what the verification receipt proved — no aspirational behavior.

